data.text:
MICHAEL STOCKL

Michael is founder and owner of GFTeam Bondi. He holds a second degree black belt in Brazilian Jiu Jitsu. He is also an experienced fitness instructor and personal trainer, with over a decade experience in the fitness industry. He has studied martial arts since childhood and his values are deeply rooted in the traditional culture of martial arts. He has a passion and skill for teaching and sharing his knowledge with his students.

DIEGO BARRETO

Diego is the head of GFTeam NSW. He holds a 2nd degree black belt in Brazilian Jiu Jitsu and a 4th degree black belt in Judo. He is well accomplished at the international level across both disciplines. He is a former member of the Brazilian National Judo team and also a former member of the Australian National Judo team.

Diego brings a wealth of knowledge, experience and a well-rounded view to our team.

He runs several GFTeam affiliates, Grappling Bros (GFTeam) Wollongong, Rockdale and Rydalmere.
